Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.rohit.sizebook.Person

  • public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Rohit on 2017-02-05. The person class provides methods and attributes for a person object Each person object is stored in an arraylist which the main app iterates over
